                <li>Estimate actual number of Pasifika people in 2023</li>
                <li>Research: Which Pacific nations contribute most to NZ population?</li>
                <li>Discuss: How does this connect to NZ's Pacific partnerships?</li>
            </ol>
            <h3>Record Your Findings:</h3>
            <div style="border: 2px dashed #666; min-height: 100px; margin-top: 1rem; background: white;"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="page-break"></div>

        <div class="station-card" style="background: #f0fdf4;">
            <h2>Station 3: Asian Communities 游꿂</h2>
            <p><strong>Focus:</strong> Asian population trends</p>
            <h3>Your Tasks:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Why did Asian population have largest percentage point increase (+2.2pp)?</li>
                <li>Calculate Asian population in actual numbers for 2023</li>
                <li>Research: Which Asian countries contribute most to NZ immigration?</li>
                <li>Discuss: How does cultural diversity benefit New Zealand?</li>
            </ol>
            <h3>Record Your Findings:</h3>
            <div style="border: 2px dashed #666; min-height: 100px; margin-top: 1rem; background: white;"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="page-break"></div>

        <div class="station-card" style="background: #fef7ff;">
