            <p><strong>Focus:</strong> Overall population trends</p>
            <h3>Your Tasks:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Calculate total NZ population increase (2018 to 2023)</li>
                <li>What does it mean that European/P캐keh캐 percentage decreased?</li>
                <li>Research: How is Auckland's diversity different from other regions?</li>
                <li>Discuss: What challenges and opportunities does diversity create?</li>
            </ol>
            <h3>Record Your Findings:</h3>
            <div style="border: 2px dashed #666; min-height: 100px; margin-top: 1rem; background: white;"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

